title: FSX America Gi-Scenery 2010 2.0
description:
FSX AGS 2010 - AMERICA GIGA SCENERY 
I invite all users to see this community to know: 
FSX AGS 2010 - AMERICA GIGA SCENERY (3.7 Gb) 
Complementary scenario of North, Central and South for FSX. 
Fully built with GPS database of high accuracy. 
Relief complete with plains, plateaus, hills and mountains SRTM. 
Typical vegetation based geoprocessing high definition. 
Detailed hydrography with rivers, lakes, dams, oceans are, islands and beaches. 
Built-up urban areas with parks, plazas, villages, towns and cities. 
Highways, roads, streets, railroads and access to car traffic.
